  ('bookkeeper-moex-00131', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-113-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'essay', '甲公司收到銀行對帳單並與公司帳簿核對，發現下列各事項：
